result.name: 蛇王業

reviews.text:
One of the most exotic Chinese dishes you can find in Hong Kong, and Yip has preserved the authentic taste of traditional snake meals.

The meal included various snakes, soft shell turtle, and gecko. It may sounds intimidating to some foreigners or even local people; but it is part of Chinese cuisine, and tourists can explore the other side of local culture. (TBH, it is less brutal than swallowing squirming squid in Korea, or lingchi a fish in Japan)
味道唔錯， 蛇肉多
地方细食品味道一般份量多如一席十四人食到夠。
勤懇克苦經營三代，歷久不衰，敬業樂業，可敬可賀。
好一般的選擇
